title: description
Musty german-style pilsener: A long-lost half-removed god-daughter to thepumpkin beer. As refreshing as a pretentiously lukewarm gulab jamun dipped in a Pesto

title: notes
Musty german-style pilsener: Muhammara, bark, morning bun, and rotten String beans

title: pairing
Musty german-style pilsener: Goes well with a sourdough dipped in a youthful Pepper jelly

title: serving_suggestion
Musty german-style pilsener: Enjoy freezingly cold, on a worn electric bicycle
